Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:05.29,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Two people's deductions and suspense\Nfill the gulf between love and hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.70,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I'm with Ran in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.70,0:00:08.43,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}A case begins with a movie actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:09.98,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:11.78,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.78,0:00:13.82,Narration Off,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.36,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.70,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.94,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Do you need a reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:28.32,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Does this world even {\i1}have{\i0} a God?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.32,0:02:30.13,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Are you Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:35.08,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}At least, no angel ever smiled on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:36.96,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:38.41,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Not even once...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.92,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Sharon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.99,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:44.42,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It was back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.43,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I met him...{manga: referent is Akai -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:51.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}When I went there with Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:56.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.59,0:03:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:10.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:15.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:18.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:19.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.79,0:03:21.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:22.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.71,0:03:23.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.64,0:03:26.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ran is... Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.98,0:03:31.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this? She's burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.21,0:03:32.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:33.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:36.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:38.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the hospital we're bringing in a patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:40.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:42.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To what hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.85,0:03:46.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an emergency hospital just past the Bay Bridge, isn't there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.24,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.24,0:03:54.50,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.50,0:03:56.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know a doctor there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:03:58.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll definitely be able to get her a bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we can be there in less than ten minutes if we take the squad car!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:02.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.29,0:04:03.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get the car ready! I'll be there in a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:06.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.06,0:04:07.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:12.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.78,0:04:13.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:14.77,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:17.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Hang in there! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:18.95,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Is that Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.26,0:04:23.11,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}It's embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:25.30,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He saved me again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.55,0:04:29.59,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Just like back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.69,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}Whenever I'm depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.54,0:04:35.90,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}He seems to be able to see right through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:40.64,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10}I hate to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:43.32,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}But it made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:46.19,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:06.93,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be10\fad(0,500)}Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:13.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Statue of Liberty."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:20.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or the "Goddess of Liberty," as we call it in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:24.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that New Yorkers call her "Miss Liberty", though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, why didn't you wake me up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:34.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really looking forward to seeing Manhattan at night from the Brooklyn Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:37.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And now we're almost across it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:38.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:43.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd slept on the plane,\Nyou wouldn't have fallen asleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.18,0:05:46.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I sleep after that guy was killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:51.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not everyone can just drop off to sleep with the satisfaction of having solved a big case!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:54.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:59.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a lifetime will be long enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:04.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to reach the pinnacle of deduction and analysis, my dear Watson...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:13.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is the greatest date spot, and the delight of lovers throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:16.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're arguing on it? I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.72,0:06:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:23.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't supposed to be in New York until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:27.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who made us get on another plane as soon as we reached LA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:32.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly managed to get tickets to a musical that I'd given up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:34.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A musical?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:37.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:44.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Golden Apple? I hear it's popular right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.32,0:06:47.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. At Broadway's Phantom Theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:48.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At 8 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.47,0:06:51.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:00.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't there a lot more patrol cars than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:03.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. They're probably after that serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.56,0:07:05.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:09.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A serial killer that only targets young girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:12.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They say he's Japanese, but I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:19.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That man apparently only attacks after midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:23.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So long as we get to the hotel before then, we'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:25.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not even six o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:30.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you mean seven? Because of Summer Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:37.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot about Summer Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.14,0:07:41.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to set my watch ahead on the first Sunday of April!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:48.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only 40 minutes by car from here to Broadway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.51,0:07:52.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not quite seven yet,\Nso we've got plenty of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.12,0:07:56.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to meet up with the friend who got the tickets for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:08:01.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said if we got to the theatre an hour early, she'd show us around backstage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're just gonna have to forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This so-called "English Lady" you bought because you fell in love with it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:10.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,will never get you there on time, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.27,0:08:16.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've done it, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.42,0:08:21.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, grit your teeth and hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:23.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:28.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The people at the Jaguar company put everything into this E-Type when they built it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.99,0:08:30.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:33.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.28,0:09:05.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This car was in the shop for repairs just last month!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just got it back the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:12.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, the mechanic was a pro. This car's as good as new!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.74,0:09:15.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They gave her back her 276 horsepower engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:18.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,along with the steering and suspension that won Le Mans!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:31.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's tons of patrol cars here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:37.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! They were in the opposite lane,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.04,0:09:42.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so they only got a glimpse of her killer curves before she vanished into the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:46.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, can you and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:50.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty tricky up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you do it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.85,0:09:55.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.14,0:10:01.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Ran, can you come here for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:08.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, don't worry. It's only scary at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, S-Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.83,0:10:22.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.77,0:10:47.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that big a deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:51.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this {\i1}not{\i0} a big deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:04.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly an hour early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See? We got here in one piece. No sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.97,0:11:28.64,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Your license and registration, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:35.02,English,,0000,0000,0000,,40 miles over the speed limit! Are you playing Dirty Harry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.73,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we were in a hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.11,English,,0000,0000,0000,,You look familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:43.62,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you might...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:46.99,English,,0000,0000,0000,,You might have met her in some case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:49.50,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she works with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.50,English,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:54.83,English,,0000,0000,0000,,She's an undercover agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:58.55,English,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to have missed the criminal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:02.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:04.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:08.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yūsaku met him when he solved a case.\NThat's how they became friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.40,0:12:12.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Radish Redwood, a captain on the New York police force.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:16.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His Japanese is pretty good since his wife's from Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.46,0:12:24.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Radish. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.03,0:12:27.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thanking the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.53,0:12:30.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The wrong person...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:32.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to thank someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.66,0:12:34.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...thank {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to thank someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:12:59.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...thank {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharon Vineyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sha... Sharon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.61,0:13:17.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.49,0:13:21.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That police agent is a fan of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:26.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking to him while waiting for you when it came over his radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:31.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That a silver Jaguar was coming here at an unbelievable speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:36.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I had the idea to disguise myself as Inspector Radish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You better be thankful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:42.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This men's coat was quite expensive, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.09,0:13:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.73,0:13:47.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But is it all right? Everyone's looking this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:50.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine. There's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.52,0:13:53.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told everyone we were filming a movie here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:57.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw... I love you, Sharon!{er wot...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.35,0:14:01.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, mom, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:02.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.28,0:14:07.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi, you don't know her? She's one of America's most famous actresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:08.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:13.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is such a famous actress disguising as an inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.67,0:14:19.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'd just started working as an actress,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:22.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I got a part as a spy girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.37,0:14:25.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that role,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:30.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned some disguise skills from Japan's most famous magician.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.84,0:14:38.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd gotten a similar role, so she was learning from the same magician, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:44.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can't disguise myself as someone else quite as well as Sharon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:50.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everytime you put one of those things on, it looked more like a clown suit than a disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:57.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry if it's not good enough for you. I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:03.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's amazing, meeting someone so famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.51,0:15:06.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially here in New York!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should thank God for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there such a thing as God in this world?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:31.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there really were a supreme being,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.96,0:15:37.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,all righteous, hard-working people would be leading happy lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:44.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, no angel ever smiled on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.19,0:15:46.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even once...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:58.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that sad smile on her face was an omen...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of the tragedy about to unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:08.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never wanted to remember... that awful case...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:16.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.07,0:16:19.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About no angel ever smiling on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:21.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just trying to say she's had a tough life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, Sharon?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:27.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. My life's just been misery after misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.62,0:16:31.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of my screen début,\Nafter struggling for years in the biz,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:33.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost both of my parents in a fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:37.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And my husband died the day after I won my Oscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:43.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's Chris, who made her début so easily just because she was my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.20,0:16:46.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything was handed to her on a silver platter. What a difference between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:52.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't exaggerate. I know you're proud of her. You put everything into raising her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:57.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That child... I don't consider her my daughter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:01.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:04.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,While I was placing flowers on my husband's grave,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:09.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,she came up behind me, disguised perfectly as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:12.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that joke was a little too black?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:15.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think about it, Sharon, you once told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.93,0:17:19.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You taught her the art of disguise because she kept begging you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.93,0:17:25.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't spoken to her in... almost ten years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:29.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she fell in with a bad crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:32.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But enough about that. Go park your car in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.19,0:17:34.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time we went backstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:39.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our audience is beginning to catch on that there's no camera rolling.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:45.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd we have to show up an hour before the musical starts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Couldn't we have come by earlier, when the actors wouldn't have been so busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:52.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we could actually talk to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.34,0:17:53.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:57.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd come here earlier, the performers would still be just regular people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:18:00.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But right before the show starts...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}Lila Sanchez (32)\NStage Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}Akane Nilsen (27)\NStage Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}Rose Hewitt (28)\NStage Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(180,0)}Night Baroness
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:14.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}If it isn't Sharon! You really made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}I guess our director {\i1}does{\i0} say the truth sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:21.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}How exciting, I feel like I'm dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you found the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you free today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:26.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, let's!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:26.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.54,0:18:31.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is when they've got their stage makeup on and they really look like actresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.29,0:18:36.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody admires her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:41.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's friends with the theater's director.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.22,0:18:43.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she wanted to come and give them her support,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:46.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and was given the tickets, just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.63,0:18:50.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Could she be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.73,0:18:55.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The popular female TV detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Night Baroness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:58.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.61,0:19:00.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(180,0)}"Night Baroness?"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what they call Mom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.12,0:19:10.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's the wife of the Night Baron's creator, Yūsaku Kudō.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:14.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And she was once invited to a local investigation show on TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.55,0:19:17.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,since she's married to a deduction genius and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:22.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She analysed the crime then, and everything she said fit,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.48,0:19:24.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,so they arrested the criminal right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:30.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how she got the nickname of the popular woman detective Night Baroness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.85,0:19:37.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though, that deduction was really just repeating what Dad said
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:40.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,every day when reading the morning paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.44,0:19:45.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then those two are your kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He is, but she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.74,0:19:53.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she might be my future daughter-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.75,0:19:55.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How marvelous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.65,0:20:06.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I thought the Night Baroness'd come to solve
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:09.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the mystery of the strange present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.53,0:20:12.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I see she's only here to greet us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)}Everith Hamilton (30)\NStage Actress
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.92,0:20:15.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Strange present?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.15,0:20:19.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.81,0:20:23.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three days ago, a packet was delivered to the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:28.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,An apple covered in gold spray. A Golden Apple.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(220,0)}«For the Fairest»
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:35.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With a message in animal blood: "For the Fairest."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.96,0:20:37.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.96,0:20:44.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That explains why I felt so much tension when I entered this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:48.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, calm down, my goddesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,150)}Heath Flockhart (33)\NStage Actor
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:51.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.61,0:20:53.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Heath...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:54.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:58.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This theater company's top star, Heath Flockhart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:03.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But since he got a part in a movie, today's his last theater play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.74,0:21:08.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everybody cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:12.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all give Sharon and her friends the backstage tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.89,0:21:23.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But is this really all right? There's only 40 minutes left, should we be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:29.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. The first 20 minutes of the play are a narration,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:32.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,where the narrator talks about Greek mythology.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.37,0:21:36.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:40.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The costumes for the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.12,0:21:42.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're up there so they won't get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:51.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.12,0:21:52.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.88,0:22:20.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:23.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.34,0:24:01.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.68,0:24:08.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, take care of Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:10.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shin{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.52,0:24:13.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.22,0:24:16.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Figured I wouldn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.95,0:24:19.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A bullet casing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.18,0:24:23.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.60,0:24:30.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan: Shin'ichi Kudo's New York Case (The Deduction)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.57,0:24:35.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Feather
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.57,0:24:36.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,さぁ、バリバリ推理するぞぉ！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.77,0:24:39.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,次回じゅうに解決しないと、また小さくなっちゃうわよ♪
